lead_paragraph: Jeff Wilpon says he thinks Yoenis Cespedes' decision to stay with the New York Mets signals a change in how the often-struggling team is viewed.

headline.print_headline: Jeff Wilpon: Mets 'Destination Now Where Players Want to Be'
